<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Transaction approuvee - {{appName}}</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #e8eaed;
      padding: 16px;
    }

    .email-container {
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(60,64,67,0.3), 0 1px 3px 1px rgba(60,64,67,0.15);
    }

    .header { padding: 28px 32px 20px; text-align: center; }
    .header-info { background-color: #1a73e8; }
    .header-success { background-color: #1e8e3e; }
    .header-warning { background-color: #f9ab00; }
    .header-error { background-color: #d93025; }

    .header h1 { color: #ffffff; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.2px; line-height: 1.3; }
    .header p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 4px; }

    .content { padding: 28px 32px 20px; }

    .greeting { font-size: 14px; color: #202124; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.6; }
    .message { font-size: 14px; color: #5f6368; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 24px; }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; color: #80868b; text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .details-card { background: #f8f9fa; border: 1px solid #dadce0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 0 16px; }

    .detail-row {
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px 0;
      font-size: 14px; color: #5f6368; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8eaed;
    }
    .detail-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .label { color: #5f6368; }
    .value { color: #202124; font-weight: 500; text-align: right; }

    .status-box {
      padding: 14px 16px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .status-box strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; }
    .status-info { background: #e8f0fe; color: #174ea6; }
    .status-success { background: #e6f4ea; color: #1e7e34; }
    .status-warning { background: #fef7e0; color: #5f4b00; }
    .status-error { background: #fce8e6; color: #a50e0e; }

    .button-container { text-align: center; margin: 24px 0; }

    .button {
      display: inline-block; background: #1a73e8; color: #ffffff;
      padding: 10px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px;
    }
    .button:hover { background: #1557b0; }

    .approver-card {
      background: #f8f9fa; border: 1px solid #dadce0;
      border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px 16px; margin: 20px 0;
      font-size: 13px; color: #5f6368; line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .approver-card strong { color: #202124; }

    .next-steps {
      background: #f8f9fa; border: 1px solid #dadce0;
      padding: 16px 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 13px; color: #5f6368; line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .next-steps ol { margin-left: 18px; }
    .next-steps li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .next-steps li:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

    .reason-text {
      background: #ffffff; border-left: 3px solid #d93025;
      padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 4px; color: #202124; font-size: 13px;
    }

    .info-card {
      background: #f8f9fa; border: 1px solid #dadce0;
      border-radius: 8px; padding: 0 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .info-row {
      display: flex; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8eaed;
      font-size: 14px; color: #5f6368;
    }
    .info-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .info-label { font-weight: 500; color: #202124; min-width: 130px; }
    .info-value { color: #5f6368; }

    .support {
      text-align: center; font-size: 13px; color: #5f6368;
      line-height: 1.8; margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 16px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e8eaed;
    }
    .support a { color: #1a73e8; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }

    .footer {
      padding: 16px 32px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px;
      color: #80868b; line-height: 1.8; background: #f8f9fa;
      border-top: 1px solid #dadce0;
    }
    .footer a { color: #5f6368; text-decoration: none; }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .header { padding: 24px 20px 16px; }
      .header h1 { font-size: 18px; }
      .content { padding: 24px 20px 16px; }
      .footer { padding: 16px 20px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="header header-success">
      <h1>Transaction approuvee</h1>
      <p>Transaction #{{transactionNumber}}</p>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p class="greeting">Bonjour {{recipientName}},</p>
      <p class="message">Nous vous confirmons que votre transaction a ete examinee et approuvee avec succes.</p>

      <div class="status-box status-success">
        <strong>Transaction approuvee</strong>
        Votre transaction #{{transactionNumber}} a ete approuvee avec succes par {{approverName}}.
      </div>

      <h2 class="section-title">Details de la transaction</h2>
      <div class="details-card">
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span class="label">Numero : </span>
          <span class="value">#{{transactionNumber}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span class="label">Type : </span>
          <span class="value">{{transactionType}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span class="label">Produit : </span>
          <span class="value">{{productName}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span class="label">Quantite : </span>
          <span class="value">{{quantity}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span class="label">Date d'approbation : </span>
          <span class="value">{{currentDate}}</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="section-title">Suivi</h2>
      <div class="approver-card">
        <strong>Approuve par : </strong> {{approverName}}<br />
        <strong>Statut : </strong> APPROUVEE<br />
        Votre transaction est desormais active et ses effets sont appliques dans le systeme.
      </div>

      <h2 class="section-title">Prochaines etapes</h2>
      <div class="next-steps">
        <ol>
          <li>La transaction est maintenant completement active</li>
          <li>Tous les mouvements ont ete appliques</li>
          <li>Consultez les details dans votre tableau de bord</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="status-box status-info">
        <strong>Conservation</strong>
        Conservez ce numero de transaction #{{transactionNumber}} pour vos dossiers.
      </div>

      <div class="button-container">
        <a href="{{dashboardLink}}" class="button">Acceder au tableau de bord</a>
      </div>

      <div class="support">
        <strong>Besoin d'aide ?</strong><br />
        <a href="{{supportLink}}">Assistance</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2026 {{appName}}. Tous droits reserves.</p>
      <p><a href="{{dashboardLink}}">Tableau de bord</a> &middot; <a href="{{supportLink}}">Assistance</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
